Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! {\alpha&HFF&}W-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! W-{\alpha&HFF&}What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.95,0:00:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! W-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, {\alpha&HFF&}the Shiniga--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, the Shiniga--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:42.98,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,0)\fs72\pos(372,380)}Reincarnation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! {\alpha&HFF&}Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lied about this being a live worldwide broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This announcement is currently being broadcast across the Kanto region of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first victim was, in fact, the Phantom Killer in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:01:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, that incident was only reported within Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.07,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just heard that the culprit was found dead in the nursery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:00.49,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it looks like the culprit is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just those pieces of information were enough for me to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that you are in Japan, and that that criminal was your first "experiment".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:12.71,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(359,333)}The Investigative Headquarters for Countermeasures Against Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is able to access confidential police files.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 141 people within the police who have access to information regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.30,0:01:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But within the 141 people {\alpha&HFF&}or people close to them... Kira will definitely be among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But within the 141 people or people close to them... {\alpha&HFF&}Kira will definitely be among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But within the 141 people or people close to them... Kira will definitely be among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:35.94,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(98,383)}FBI investigation into those connected to the Japanese Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the 14th of December, twelve FBI agents entered Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the 19th of December,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is evidently using prisoners as test subjects in order to study how they could manipulate the victims' movements before death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:50.50,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this we can deduct that to kill the FBI agents, Kira found it necessary to experiment to see how far they could manipulate someone's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.67,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:02:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consequently, Kira must be someone that was under investigation by the FBI between the 14th and the 19th.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.86,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\pos(490,354)\fad(420,0)}An important witness: \NMisora Naomi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray Penber's fianc√©e?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misora Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... {\alpha&HFF&}the girl who worked for me on that case... in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... the girl who worked for me on that case... in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently she was with Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might have discovered something...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, does this mean Kira beat me to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.14,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(355,326)}Yagami Light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone. {\alpha&HFF&}From now on, we'll only be investigating those people who were under surveillance by Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone. From now on, we'll only be investigating those people who were under surveillance by Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The subjects of our investigation will be Deputy Kitamura and his family, {\alpha&HFF&}and Chief Yagami and his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The subjects of our investigation will be Deputy Kitamura and his family, and Chief Yagami and his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:03:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd also like to be able to set up cameras and bugging devices in both households.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, don't tell me... {\alpha&HFF&}you actually suspect my son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, don't tell me... you actually suspect my son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I definitely suspect him, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.91,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(356,322)}Contact with Yagami Light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Kira hates to lose, the majority of people would want to win in a match, whether they're Kira or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See. I knew you'd want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect that you may be Kira, Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga... {\alpha&HFF&}is there any way that I can prove to you that I'm not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga... is there any way that I can prove to you that I'm not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't Kira, I'll find out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.13,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(181,451)}Murder cases \Ninvolving a TV channel \Ncooperating with Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four days ago, the director on duty received these four tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:03.56,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ratings will rise by 60.. no, 70% at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...further predictions to provide proof that they are Kira, but also a message to the people of the world:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.81,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:17.31,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,The anchorman, Hibima Kazuhiko, will die of a heart attack at exactly 6 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to stop this broadcast, or there'll be trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira doesn't have a name, they shouldn't be able to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having watched this, it seems that the probability of Kira being able to kill someone solely by knowing their face isn't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police! Stop the broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The probability of this Kira being a fake is extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\alpha&HFF&}a "second Kira" is probably a better description.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a "second Kira" is probably a better description.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, {\alpha&HFF&}would it be okay if we asked your son to help us in the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, would it be okay if we asked your son to help us in the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.60,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(174,384)}Yagami Light summoned \Nto the Investigative Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, there's a high probability that this is not the same Kira that we've been dealing with previously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as L... I mean, that's exactly the same theory as Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:06.74,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet, we can confirm our identities by showing each other our Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're using a code that only those with a Shinigami's power would understand, then I won't be able to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... we'll need to ensure that we keep a close surveillance on all the locations mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to observe Light-kun carefully during those two days as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, by any chance he really is Kira, the second Kira may attempt to approach him in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yagami-san... have Mogi-san keep a close eye on Light-kun's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.94,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(362,395)}The arrest of Amane Misa on suspicion of being the second Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Light's girlfriend, Amane Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ryuuga Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ryuuga Hideki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably both good and bad news for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've apprehended Amane Misa on suspicion of being the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the second Kira sent the video tapes from Amane's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they left a great deal of evidence, such as hairs and clothing fibres stuck to packing tape used to seal the envelopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.55,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(356,314)}Amane Misa's detention
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki... what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki... what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you could kill me in an instant if you wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that you admit you are the second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't know anything about the second Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.03,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(361,357)}The voluntary detention of Yagami Light
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, it's as I said on the phone... {\alpha&HFF&}I might be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, it's as I said on the phone... I might be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying "I might be Kira"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you "might be" Kira; you {\b1}are{\b0} Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that I look too good at the moment... but such meaningless pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I discard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! I know I chose to be imprisoned and go through with this, but I've just realized, I am not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two weeks' worth of criminals were taken out in one shot yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx266.25\fscy100\pos(412,174)\c&HB8BABC&\3c&H484A4C&}Kira Returns
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.49,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(358,304)}The prisoners released
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like all three of them are reaching their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, why do you continue to detain Light-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been fifty days!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill you here and then I'll kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, father?! Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Dad! You're crazy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, father! I'm not Kira!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... {\alpha&HFF&}we're both murderers; see you in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... we're both murderers; see you in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a very realistic performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, I'll end their imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:57.33,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(94,383)}Yagami Light, summoned again under \Nthe pretext of helping with the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also Light-kun, as promised, I'm prepared to make a pact with you; that is, you'll be with me 24/7 assisting me with this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.51,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,315)}Yotsuba
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are deaths that have benefited Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you dig a little deeper, there have been thirteen incidents over the last three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.64,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(355,307)}The infiltration of Yotsuba
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kira a part of Yotsuba? {\alpha&HFF&}Is Kira merely using Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kira a part of Yotsuba? Is Kira merely using Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no idea which it is, but we can assume that Kira is behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time that we investigate Yotsuba thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, think ahead carefully before you act, and don't do anything rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just act on your own judgments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Matsui Tarou, a manager at Yoshida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you like to hire our star, Amane Misa, for your commercials?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eight that are here were in a meeting together, planning who to have Kira murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Matsuda-san dies now, it will confirm the suspicions surrounding Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really no way to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.93,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(176,382)}The conclusion that \NHiguchi Kyousuke is Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Misa-Misa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and prepare the celebrations for when you land this commercial!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa's dream is to become Kira's wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Misa is... the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I'm Kira, you'd better marry me, Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, as you can all hear... Higuchi is Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.78,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,346)}Higuchi's capture
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use Sakura TV to trap Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Dokkiri TV?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi, this looks bad. Turn on your TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one of those is Kira, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and I have plenty of proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him! Why is he still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi's status confirmed. I'm in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You in the Porsche! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull over to the side! Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, it's time to do the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Deal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were speeding. Let's see your license.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to shake off the cop! He's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Traffic Riot Police--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! I believe it will be too dangerous to allow Higuchi to act any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going ahead with his capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Higuchi is now able to kill just by looking at someone's face, similar to the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be making the arrest under that assumption!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back! No one come near!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.03,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(356,307)}Higuchi captured
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi, how were you killing people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably won't believe me, but if you write the name of a person whose face you know in that notebook, that person will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it in his bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yagami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than one notebook exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.77,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(168,379)}The Death Note, \Nand the analysis of its rules
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How to use"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The human whose name is written in this note shall die."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this final sentence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"From the moment a new user writes a name into this notebook, they must continue to write names, each within 13 days of the last; otherwise, the user will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light and Amane Misa are still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13 days... this is the only thing...
Comment: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki has been dead for ten days now; {\alpha&HFF&}seems like we've managed to avoid being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki has been dead for ten days now; seems like we've managed to avoid being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've managed to find a little about Watari's true identity, but we've found nothing about Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Watari turned out to be an incredible inventor, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He established orphanages all over the world using the fortune he made from his patents."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a great man! A great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:12:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}with L and Watari gone, we can't continue our investigations from here. It's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, with L and Watari gone, {\alpha&HFF&}we can't continue our investigations from here. It's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, with L and Watari gone, we can't continue our investigations from here. {\alpha&HFF&}It's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, with L and Watari gone, we can't continue our investigations from here. It's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light? {\alpha&HFF&}How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light? How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to remove and take most of the system with us by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't feel good doing this though, it's like being a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've managed to create a voice identical to the one Ryuuzaki was using;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to make it seem like he's still alive, and we can control the world's police forces just as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I don't know who'll take L's place or where... or what we're supposed to do with this murderer's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Light-kun? {\alpha&HFF&}The only one who can take on the role of L is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Light-kun? The only one who can take on the role of L is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ryuuzaki died as a result of provoking Kira, it's not exactly a tempting position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it means we're deceiving the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, Light-kun, but besides you, there's no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. Even Ryuuzaki said, "Light-kun would be able to succeed me".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So easy... {\alpha&HFF&}just as I predicted, without Ryuuzaki around, it's so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So easy... just as I predicted, without Ryuuzaki around, it's so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But unlike Ryuuzaki, I won't be using any dangerous methods such as challenging Kira in order to gain hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're all okay with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's probably better to err on the side of caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki was probably a little too confrontational.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I can manage with just this PC and my own, so it'll be possible for me to act as L from my own room at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll act as Watari as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's going to be rather difficult with my mother and sister around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be useful if I could rent a single room somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you an allowance to live on your own. No one will find that odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. Well, from now on, Light-kun's room will be the new investigative headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all that's left is to decide what to do with the murderer's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't need to think too hard about that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to keep it in an unknown location. So have one of us five, someone we trust will never use it, hide it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, please do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief can definitely do it. He's full of righteousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? {\alpha&HFF&}Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's avenge Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is still on the loose. We must catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't we hold a party to celebrate Light-kun becoming the second L?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! This is our first date in a while, you could at least try to look a little happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've already rented an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! We're going to live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa wins!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over Kiyomi, Mari, Yuri and so on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Light. I understood that you were just using them to deceive L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be seeing them anymore, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you've completely settled the score with L, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I won't have much fun to look forward to then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm going to show you the reincarnation of a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on... I'm going to show you the reincarnation of a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reconstruction of Yotsuba begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-{\alpha&HFF&}Yes, let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey? {\alpha&HFF&}Namikawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey? Namikawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Surely not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Surely not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,April 2012: {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Light, aged 23, joins the National Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,April 2012: Yagami Light, aged 23, joins the National Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer 2012: {\alpha&HFF&}The rate of Kira's judgment increases even more rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer 2012: The rate of Kira's judgment increases even more rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world becomes split into two groups: those that scream in fear at Kira, and those that secretly cheer him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little, those voices in support of Kira begin to surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, entire countries begin to declare their acceptance of Kira's work,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the world continues to head toward a dark age, where Kira is law.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L... {\alpha&HFF&}has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L... has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.84,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(562,298)}To be continued
